reviewText: Just OK. John is a good coach, but too much focus on Bruce and too little instructional detail from John. You can tell that spending a couple hours with John would be a very good thing, but the DVD falls short.
I liked this dvd, i found it full of useful infomation. Now i have to put to use
Best video for clay shooting.  I have watched many Sunrise video's but John Woolley's approach is spot on.  I have improved from 50-60% to 90%+.  No magic.  Good common sense.
Very informative. Teaches the basics you need to know to become a better shooter! Shows the small things that are important in your approach to the target
